                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "Each use case identifies pre-conditions and alternative behavior if the pre-conditions are not met, such as looking for a lost book; post-conditions, which summarize the effects of the use case; and a normal, error-free scenario comprising a sequence of steps performed by actors or by the system.",
