                "content": "Training and documentation can be planned as soon as the requirements analysis is complete.",
                "img_id": null
            },
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "The development team can put in place ways to access updates from a central location or to download them to users automatically from the Internet or Web sites.",
